snippet.title: Elsa Anna Arendelle
snippet.description:
This channel is primarily devoted to making mashups and montages of various films and songs.

A sizable portion is devoted to Frozen 1 and 2. The first Frozen film is one of my favorite films and it was just done so well.

I also make mashups of other Disney films, most notably using a song from a particular animated movie and adapting it to the live action version. 

80's music is one of my favorite genres.
